  "title": "Xtra Crispy Slovakian Casabe Wrap",
  "description": "A sweet and crispy Slovakian dish featuring casabe, perfect for curing hangovers, wrapped in a corn husk wrap and filled with coconut cream crack, dairy free friendly.",
