  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Toast the casabe pieces for 5 minutes on each side.",
    "Mix the coconut cream, coconut oil, maple syrup, and vanilla extract in a bowl.",
    "Spread the coconut cream mixture on each toasted casabe piece.",
    "Sprinkle shredded coconut and salt on top of the coconut cream mixture.",
    "Wrap each casabe piece in a corn husk wrap.",
    "Bake the wrapped casabe for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
